ime":"2021-02-17T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"炸牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ec5dd7419e486f1f32da5eee66340f41c7dfa6","tid":2411691,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"[廚房Gear撚 Part 1] 新手入廚房跟我買哩8樣嘢就夠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409371</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第一版睇不鏽鋼<br />\n但我最愛cast iron skillet (Lodge)來煎肉，但不鏽鋼可以有fond做pan sauce<br />\n<br />\n你個任務係整到表面超乾，先會煎得靚<br />\n- 用廚房紙抹到超乾，由鹽餣過夜<br />\n- 再用廚房紙抹到超乾<br />\n- 擺係室溫半個鐘<br />\n- 用vegetable oil (smoking point高）<br />\n- 油熱到少少出煙先夠熱<br />\n- 每面30秒反（咁樣可以均勻受熱）<br />\n- 加牛油用匙羹basting (牛油smoking point不夠高，一開始落會焦哂都未夠熱）<br />\n- 買支探熱針，130F上碟(medium rare)<br />\n<br />\n有支sous vide棒更正！"},{"pid":"99d7f55fe54d5b239311551ce6671bf65fdc6b4f","tid":2411691,"uid":381621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ec5dd7419e486f1f32da5eee66340f41c7dfa6","tid":2411691,"uid":392377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"[廚房Gear撚 Part 1] 新手入廚房跟我買哩8樣嘢就夠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409371</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第一版睇不鏽鋼<br />\n但我最愛cast iron skillet (Lodge)來煎肉，但不鏽鋼可以有fond做pan sauce<br />\n<br />\n你個任務係整到表面超乾，先會煎得靚<br />\n- 用廚房紙抹到超乾，由鹽餣過夜<br />\n- 再用廚房紙抹到超乾<br />\n- 擺係室溫半個鐘<br />\n- 用vegetable oil (smoking point高）<br />\n- 油熱到少少出煙先夠熱<br />\n- 每面30秒反（咁樣可以均勻受熱）<br />\n- 加牛油用匙羹basting (牛油smoking point不夠高，一開始落會焦哂都未夠熱）<br />\n- 買支探熱針，130F上碟(medium rare)<br />\n<br />\n有支sous vide棒更正！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLodge隻生鐵pan好似幾抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8570e86e916068d3db1e6d12c2c5afc3612f03cf","tid":2411691,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ec5dd7419e